  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ChangeAnalyzerException
    Base class for all ChangeAnalyzer exceptions.
    DataSetBuilderException
    Exception thrown by DataSetBuilder class.
    ExtractionException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs during extraction of information from a repository.
    PredictionException
    Exception thrown due to an error in performing bug-proneness prediction.
    ProcessingException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs during processing a data set.
